| Field    | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| id       | int(11)     | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| btitle   | varchar(20) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| pub_date | datetime(6) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| bread    | int(11)     | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| bcommet  | int(11)     | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| isDelete | tinyint(1)  | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
