05 模型类的创建方法
 python manage.py  shell 

>>> from booktest.models import BookInfo
>>> from datetime import datetime 

>>> b=BookInfo.create('abc',datetime(1990,1,1))
>>> b.save()

MariaDB [(none)]> use test2;

MariaDB [test2]> select * from bookinfo;
